RUNNING THE POST-PROCESSING PROGRAMS (SEE ITEM 06016)

Having run FPIBE and obtained a file BFLOW.RES which
contains sensible looking results, the post-processing programs
should run simply by entering the command PPDRAG.BAT

Results should then be found in OVDRAG.RES.

The program structure and names in PPDRAG.RES differ slightly from
those detailed in Item 06016. This should cause no problems, but if
difficulties are encountered, please contact ESDU.
                                            

